00:14:17.459 --> 00:14:18.822
Simplificando,

00:14:18.826 --> 00:14:21.122
precisamos ser abertos e colaboradores.

00:14:21.696 --> 00:14:22.831
Obrigado.

00:14:22.831 --> 00:14:24.783
(Aplausos)

